solution: ```class Solution {
    public int minAddToMakeValid(String s) {
        int openNeeded = 0;
        int balance = 0;
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            if (c == '(') {
                balance++;
            } else {
                if (balance > 0) {
                    balance--;
                } else {
                    openNeeded++;
                }
            }
        }
        return openNeeded + balance;
    }
}
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Single left-to-right pass tracks unmatched open and close parentheses; unmatched opens are stored in balance, unmatched closes in openNeeded. Sum gives minimal insertions.

